MOTORCYCLE CRASH KILLS WOMAN, INJURES MAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A motorcycle accident Sunday on a curve near Palmdale severely injured the 
driver and killed a woman passenger. 
</P>
<P>
California Highway Patrol Officer Scott Davis said the two people were thrown 
from the motorcycle after the driver was unable to negotiate a curve and hit a 
curb on 90th Street East, south of Avenue S, at 2:45 a.m. 
</P>
