<P>
San Diego police were investigating the death of an unidentified teen-ager who 
witnesses say was pushed out of a moving vehicle Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
The victim, a Latina about 11 to 12 years old, was reportedly shoved out of a 
car traveling north on Interstate 5 near Old Town about 1:30 a.m., Deputy 
