and jazz instructors to the inner city. The Plaza program will culminate with a 
bilingual production of Thornton Wilder's "Our Town" called "Nuestro Barrio" 
next spring. CalArts jazz instructors and master students will work with eight 
high schools in the Watts Towers area to eventually present two jazz concerts 
next spring and possibly form a high school jazz band. GREG BRAXTON 
