Emerson Fittipaldi for his 10th career CART victory -- all on street courses. 
KIRK McKOY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Al Unser Jr. led 91 of the race's 95 
laps along the 1.67-mile, twisting Long Beach street course. LORI SHEPLER / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
